nies house info employees linked domains short description baillie gifford are longterm investors not speculators our investment philosophy focuses on growth while our universe is global in equities our belief is that sustained growth in company profits leads to higher share prices over time in bonds we take a differentiated investment approach which focuses on longterm prospects rather than the potential for shortterm price movements baillie gifford was founded in  and is an independent investment manager managing pension funds investment trusts unit trusts and isas at baillie gifford existing clients interests are paramount and we frequently close our products to new business to ensure that the integrity of our strategies and the quality of service are maintained this commitment to professional excellence ensures clients receive our full attentionthanks to our partnership structure we are free to focus entirely on our longterm vision to deliver the best results for our clients without the distraction of shortterm shareholder demands contact info access baillie giffords contact information contact information summary website wwwbailliegiffordcom emails  employee emails  telephone numbers  locations registered addresses f one international finance centre  harbour view street central hong kong    fax    phone  third avenue th floor new york ny      fax     phone calton square  greenside row edinburgh eh an      fax     phone calton square  greenside row edinburgh eh an scotland united kingdom want access to baillie gifford’s other addresses including old address information signup now for free and access the following information additional addresses  former addresses  employees at baillie gifford get instant access to baillie gifford’s employee data with biographies and contact information employee data summary senior employees  other employees  employee contacts  former employees  additional info id  matchdeck number  company category private limited company compan